  "instructions": [
    "Heat the hot stone plate over medium heat until it is hot.",
    "Add the vegetable oil and sauté the diced onion until translucent.",
    "Stir in the minced garlic, grated ginger, and chopped chili, cooking for 1 minute.",
    "Mix in the curry paste, turmeric powder, and a splash of coconut milk, letting the mixture simmer.",
    "Add the buchu leaves, mint leaves, and diced tomato, stirring until the herbs wilt.",
